Invocation Name: multiplication ones
des: This skill is help you master your one time multiplication tables. You can review the flash cards and then test your knowledge. At any point you can say "Alexa, review mode" to switch to review or say "Alexa, test mode" to start a test. You can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next card. At any point during the test, you can say "Alexa, what's my score" to get your current test score. Thank you for using this skill and hope you use my other skills ....
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
